title._content: United States fleet underway at San Francisco, 1920-1930

description._content:
The ANMM undertakes research and accepts public comments that enhance the information we hold about images in our collection. This record has been updated accordingly. 

This photograph is part of the Henry Stewart collection, which was originally part of the Australian War Memorial and was transferred to the ANMM.

Object no. ANMS0047[090]
